<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Krista Thuokna!</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Kalvari tang chunga Lalpa chuh,
 Kraws chunga linglukhuk tawh;
 Mipite nuihsan dingin,
 Thinglek ah a khai kang ui.

[V2]
 Aw a na na zen e,
 I Lalpau a bawlnau chu;
 A khut A keng, A lu en un,
 I gitloh ziek, A thisan,
 Thiengtho chu a va zo tai,
 A thuokgim lawm lawm ngei.

[V3]
 2. Ka dang a chak tin A kiko khan,
 Zu thuk a dawn sak ui;
 Zu thuk chun suhai puona,
 Thagau ngaia cha'k a hi.

[V4]
 3. A thihkuon a dangchak lai khan,
 Kuoman a pie nuom puou hi;
 Melma simsen loh lakah,
 Dangchak mahmah in a thii.

[V5]
 4. Aw ka thagau, na tatna natzie,
 Ken vang ka hun hilh thei puoi;
 Chieh in Kalvari tanga,
 Na Lalpa khu va tulh in.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>71</hymn_number>
<author>VT. Kappu</author>
</song>